01:11:26.920 --> 01:11:28.240
And other questions about this?

01:11:31.520 --> 01:11:32.810
OK.

01:11:32.810 --> 01:11:34.940
What could go wrong?

01:11:34.940 --> 01:11:35.964
What could go wrong?

