a couple of things

01:12:54.994 --> 01:12:56.782
that are above the background.

01:12:56.782 --> 01:12:58.130
And they don't necessarily--

01:12:58.130 --> 01:12:58.838
PROFESSOR: Right.

01:12:58.838 --> 01:13:00.500
So is it maybe
